paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the role of C1QA and C1QC genes in modifying age-at-onset in TTR-FAP Val30Met patients. No new TTR variants are reported.

challenges: The paper focused on C1QA and C1QC genes, not TTR variants.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper did not report any new variants in the TTR gene. It focused on genetic modifiers of age-at-onset in TTR-FAP Val30Met patients.
